title: PML-N’s Muhammad Hanif Abbasi wins NA-56 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan Muslim League-Nawaz (PML-N) Candidate Muhammad Hanif Abbasi has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-56 Rawalpindi-V by securing 96,649 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Independent candidate Shehryar Riaz, who bagged 82,613 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 44.84 percent.
